18:58.687 --> 19:00.365
How many people did
you have under surveillance

19:00.389 --> 19:02.221
when you were first lady?

19:03.491 --> 19:05.091
Why did you meet with him?

19:05.126 --> 19:06.192
Is that against the law?

19:06.227 --> 19:08.727
I could be, depending on
what you talked about.

19:11.132 --> 19:12.431
He's telling the truth.

