Let's go!

35:28.494 --> 35:30.527
Open it.

35:33.732 --> 35:35.532
(whispering): Shit.

35:35.567 --> 35:37.233
Shit.

35:37.269 --> 35:38.435
The-the battery's dead.

35:38.470 --> 35:40.236
What is this, some kind of a joke?

35:40.272 --> 35:41.905
Uh, I-I can't.

35:41.940 --> 35:44.274
- I-I can't.
- Do you think I'm an idiot?

36:12.988 --> 36:15.388
Where were you?

36:19.462 --> 36:20.694
Been here for an hour.

36:20.730 --> 36:22.929
You didn't answer your phone.

36:25.701 --> 36:26.701
Wine?

36:26.736 --> 36:29.035
You look like you could use some.

36:33.509 --> 36:35.309
It's Quintarelli.

36:35.344 --> 36:38.078
Yeah, well, it's all grape juice to me.

36:50.024 --> 36:52.224
You missed your window.

36:52.260 --> 36:53.593
I have to go.

36:53.628 --> 36:56.396
Watch your television tonight.

36:56.431 --> 36:58.398
Why? What have you got up your sleeve?

36:58.433 --> 37:00.700
You advise the government.

37:00.735 --> 37:02.802
You know I can't talk to you about that.

37:06.341 --> 37:07.973
(sighs)

37:19.152 --> 37:20.985
I'm Nafisa Al-Qadi.

37:21.021 --> 37:23.154
Pleasure to meet you.

37:23.190 --> 37:25.490
This is my sister, Safiya.

37:25.526 --> 37:28.727
You and I should, uh, spend
some time together.

37:28.762 --> 37:30.662
Get to know each other.

37:31.765 --> 37:34.132
You're supposed to
say, "That will be nice."

37:34.167 --> 37:37.001
I prefer honest to polite.

37:37.037 --> 37:38.236
I believe you're using

37:38.271 --> 37:40.038
my husband.

37:40.073 --> 37:42.641
We're using each other.

37:42.676 --> 37:44.843
Given the history of
my people and yours,

37:44.878 --> 37:46.778
it's not as neat as you make it sound.

37:46.814 --> 37:48.880
History's about to change,

37:48.915 --> 37:51.716
but I appreciate a woman
who supports her husband.

37:51.751 --> 37:53.885
Like you did, Mrs. Al Fayeed?

37:55.222 --> 37:57.388
It's time, madam.

37:57.423 --> 37:59.490
(quietly): Thank you.

38:02.896 --> 38:04.863
<i>For generations</i>

38:04.898 --> 38:07.165
the secular and the religious

38:07.200 --> 38:12.103
have lived separate
existences in our country.

38:12.138 --> 38:15.406
Today we know

38:15.441 --> 38:18.943
that is no longer possible...

38:18.979 --> 38:23.213
if our nation is
going to have a real future.

38:23.249 --> 38:25.115
And so, today,

38:25.150 --> 38:26.450
I stand here,

38:26.486 --> 38:29.186
proud...

38:29.221 --> 38:32.256
to announce a coalition

38:32.291 --> 38:34.658
that will finally unite

38:34.694 --> 38:36.560
all of our people.

38:36.596 --> 38:40.130
A coalition of harmony.

38:40.165 --> 38:42.833
A coalition for peace.

38:52.111 --> 38:54.678
BARRY: <i>I don't know what it
is you think you're doing.</i>

38:54.714 --> 38:55.913
Please, you're just upset

38:55.948 --> 38:57.214
your guy isn't going to win.

38:59.719 --> 39:02.152
I banned that man from office,

39:02.187 --> 39:03.887
and you defied me.

39:03.923 --> 39:05.700
I'm not having this conversation
with you again.

39:05.724 --> 39:07.068
Is it just that you need to hurt me?

39:07.092 --> 39:07.824
Is that it?

39:07.859 --> 39:09.626
You still hate me that much?

39:09.661 --> 39:10.794
You can't really think that.

39:10.829 --> 39:12.529
Tell me how else I should interpret it.

39:12.564 --> 39:14.331
I never want to hurt you.

39:14.366 --> 39:16.133
- Never.
- Bullshit.

39:16.168 --> 39:18.101
You're lying.

39:18.137 --> 39:20.570
You're always lying.

39:20.605 --> 39:22.306
I'm not. I'm not lying.

39:22.341 --> 39:23.773
I'm not trying to betray you.

39:23.809 --> 39:25.708
I'm not your enemy.

39:25.744 --> 39:27.710
I just disagree with you.

39:27.746 --> 39:30.613
Not everyone who
disagrees with you is a traitor.

39:30.649 --> 39:34.418
He embraced my daughter's murderer,

39:34.453 --> 39:38.088
and you made him a partner.

39:38.123 --> 39:40.790
(short laugh)

39:42.094 --> 39:43.593
Get out.

39:43.628 --> 39:46.796
I never want to see your face again.

39:49.601 --> 39:52.368
Get out.

39:52.403 --> 39:53.870
No, you can't do that.

39:53.905 --> 39:57.774
You may be angry, but you
can't walk away from me.

39:58.810 --> 40:00.877
We're connected, you and I.

40:00.912 --> 40:02.912
(scoffs) That was a long time ago.

40:02.948 --> 40:04.681
- Not that.
- And Jamal is dead.

40:04.716 --> 40:06.483
Not that, either.

40:06.518 --> 40:09.786
What the hell are you talking about?

40:10.755 --> 40:12.421
Our child.

40:13.257 --> 40:14.257
Our son.

40:15.193 --> 40:17.626
Don't tell me you never suspected.

40:17.661 --> 40:21.463
The weekend before my wedding.

40:21.499 --> 40:23.164
Don't tell me you don't remember.

40:23.200 --> 40:27.669
I held onto it for so many years.

40:27.705 --> 40:30.873
I wanted to tell you desperately.

40:30.908 --> 40:34.209
When you came back for Ahmed's wedding.

40:34.244 --> 40:36.745
I wanted to tell you it was your son

40:36.780 --> 40:38.446
who was about to exchange vows.

40:38.482 --> 40:40.048
But for Ahmed's sake,

40:40.083 --> 40:42.450
I had to protect him from your brother.

40:42.486 --> 40:44.753
So there was no way I could.

40:44.788 --> 40:47.122
You would've done the same.

40:47.157 --> 40:48.857
We may disagree,

40:48.893 --> 40:52.292
we may never see eye to
eye politically ever again,

40:52.328 --> 40:54.428
but we're connected.

40:56.533 --> 40:58.766
It's all legacy.

40:58.801 --> 41:01.636
A legacy of love.

41:01.671 --> 41:04.872
Mine, at least.

41:07.043 --> 41:09.777
- (bangs on door)
- Open the door.

41:14.316 --> 41:17.823
(sighs)

41:26.433 --> 41:27.711
Apparently, there's polling

41:27.735 --> 41:29.401
that comes out later today that was done

41:29.436 --> 41:31.870
after our announcement last night.

41:33.307 --> 41:35.874
We'll see where we are.

41:37.162 --> 41:38.343
What's wrong?

41:38.378 --> 41:39.477
The kid who took

41:39.513 --> 41:41.680
those pictures of you?

41:41.716 --> 41:42.981
He was found dead.

41:43.017 --> 41:45.317
Police said robbery gone wrong...

41:45.352 --> 41:48.353
but that isn't
really what happened, is it?

41:48.388 --> 41:50.689
What are you suggesting?

41:50.725 --> 41:51.623
You tell me.

41:51.658 --> 41:53.692
I had nothing to do with it.

41:53.728 --> 41:55.293
I don't even know who that kid was.

41:55.329 --> 41:56.460
Your general then.

41:56.495 --> 41:57.773
Did you tell him about the pictures?

41:57.797 --> 41:59.063
Of course I did.

41:59.099 --> 41:59.831
So, it was him.

41:59.866 --> 42:01.899
I have no idea.

42:01.935 --> 42:03.701
Of course it was.

42:05.638 --> 42:08.505
If it was him...

42:08.541 --> 42:10.241
it was to protect me...

42:10.276 --> 42:13.277
you... us.

42:13.312 --> 42:15.646
- (slams down cup)
- Stop looking at me that way.

42:15.681 --> 42:16.759
Some people get what they deserve.

42:16.783 --> 42:18.983
He didn't deserve it.

42:19.018 --> 42:20.684
He wasn't a blackmailer.

42:20.720 --> 42:22.053
What are you talking about?

42:22.088 --> 42:24.889
I paid him to take those pictures.

42:25.725 --> 42:27.158
I don't understand.

42:27.193 --> 42:29.861
He was just a kid who worked for me.

42:29.896 --> 42:32.563
I gave him a few hundred
bucks just to scare

42:32.598 --> 42:34.998
some sense into you.

42:41.240 --> 42:43.440
Well, that was stupid, wasn't it?

42:43.476 --> 42:44.575
Who are you people?

42:44.610 --> 42:45.643
"You people"?

42:45.678 --> 42:46.977
Isn't there any limit

42:47.012 --> 42:48.457
to what you'll do to get what you want?

42:48.481 --> 42:50.247
No, this was your doing...

42:50.283 --> 42:51.348
not mine,

42:51.384 --> 42:52.149
not William's.

42:52.184 --> 42:55.352
He killed someone for no reason.

42:55.388 --> 42:57.821
Even if he was a blackmailer,

42:57.856 --> 43:00.023
I had paid him off.

43:01.627 --> 43:03.527
You need to pull yourself together.

43:03.562 --> 43:05.829
Everything is about to change for us,

43:05.864 --> 43:07.130
for all of us.

43:07.166 --> 43:09.299
I'm not going to put
that at risk because of some

43:09.334 --> 43:10.533
mistake you made.

43:10.568 --> 43:12.936
This stays between us.

43:13.872 --> 43:16.006
Between us.

43:16.041 --> 43:18.208
Or what? He kills me, too?

43:18.243 --> 43:20.443
You need to pull yourself together!

43:26.751 --> 43:27.951
Right.

43:27.986 --> 43:29.886
COGSWELL: It was an accident.

43:29.922 --> 43:32.455
I did what I had to do...

43:32.490 --> 43:35.425
to protect us, to protect you.

43:35.460 --> 43:38.528
I'm not used to being
taken care of that way.

43:39.897 --> 43:41.497
You make me feel safe.

43:41.533 --> 43:43.299
(chuckles)

43:43.335 --> 43:47.704
Well, you are many
things, Leila Al Fayeed,

43:47.739 --> 43:50.272
but safe is not one of them.

43:52.610 --> 43:54.944
Are you near a TV?

43:54.979 --> 43:57.847
(children laughing nearby)

43:57.882 --> 44:00.583
Nafisa, where's the remote?

44:01.653 --> 44:02.819
Nafisa!

44:02.854 --> 44:04.286
I'm in the refrigerator.

44:04.322 --> 44:06.055
Find it yourself.

44:08.460 --> 44:10.159
NEWSWOMAN: The latest polls in the race

44:10.194 --> 44:13.028
for president of Abuddin signified
a major change today

44:13.064 --> 44:14.308
- in the political landscape.
- You'll never catch me.

44:14.332 --> 44:15.497
I will, I will.

44:15.532 --> 44:16.966
- Quiet!
- Just one day after

44:17.001 --> 44:18.045
her announcement of a coalition

44:18.069 --> 44:19.468
with the Freedom Party

44:19.503 --> 44:20.569
of Sheik Al-Qadi,

44:20.604 --> 44:23.305
Leila Al Fayeed has pulled ahead

44:23.341 --> 44:24.974
of Fauzi Nidal,

44:25.009 --> 44:27.176
with 51% to 45%

44:27.211 --> 44:29.778
and 4% yet to be decided.

44:29.813 --> 44:31.914
Did you hear that?

44:31.949 --> 44:33.575
Did you hear that?

44:33.728 --> 44:34.962
What are you talking about?

44:34.986 --> 44:36.318
It looks like your father

44:36.354 --> 44:38.921
is going to be prime
minister of Abuddin.

44:38.956 --> 44:41.290
You see what you've done?!

44:41.325 --> 44:43.792
You've joined our enemies together.

44:43.827 --> 44:45.527
- Fauzi.
- Tell him!

44:45.562 --> 44:47.028
What are you doing here, anyway?

44:47.063 --> 44:49.230
I was delivering a Commission report.

44:49.266 --> 44:51.566
- Is that a problem?
- This is a disaster, Bassam.

44:51.602 --> 44:52.634
It's a disaster!

44:52.669 --> 44:53.702
It won't stick, Fauzi.

44:53.737 --> 44:55.069
What are the chances of them

44:55.105 --> 44:56.738
holding a coalition like this together?

44:56.774 --> 44:58.117
For two months until the election?

44:58.141 --> 44:59.708
Pretty good, I'd say.

44:59.743 --> 45:01.175
And if she gets to be president,

45:01.211 --> 45:02.744
you've amputated your own revolution.

45:02.780 --> 45:04.245
Fauzi, it's just one poll.

45:04.281 --> 45:05.792
They probably got a
bounce off the announcement.

45:05.816 --> 45:07.816
Look, let's not panic.

45:07.851 --> 45:09.028
All right? There's
still a long way to go.

45:09.052 --> 45:10.118
You just couldn't leave

45:10.153 --> 45:11.820
well enough alone, could you?

45:11.855 --> 45:13.354
You had to ban Al-Qadi.

45:13.390 --> 45:16.224
You are no different from your brother.

45:18.661 --> 45:23.331
Unless you have something
else to say, we're busy here.

45:35.711 --> 45:37.545
Don't say it.

45:38.982 --> 45:41.049
You need someone on your side.

45:42.419 --> 45:44.518
I'll be on your side.

45:52.562 --> 45:54.762
God has sent me a message.

45:54.797 --> 45:58.131
In some sense I always knew,

45:58.167 --> 46:03.070
but I let myself... be convinced.

46:03.940 --> 46:05.473
That was my mistake.

46:09.579 --> 46:11.879
My path is revenge.

46:11.914 --> 46:14.247
Nothing else.

46:15.050 --> 46:17.117
I understand.

46:28.416 --> 46:29.957
IHAB: <i>What is going on</i>

46:29.982 --> 46:32.723
in Abuddin makes it
even more important for us

46:32.748 --> 46:34.886
to put the pressure on.

46:34.921 --> 46:36.380
This American

46:36.405 --> 46:37.767
is not going to be president forever,

46:37.791 --> 46:39.924
and before he steps aside,

46:39.960 --> 46:42.816
we need to encourage him to
make a war he's going to regret.

46:42.841 --> 46:44.917
Your plan for Al-Qadi backfired.

46:45.069 --> 46:47.183
Instead of making the
American more powerful,

46:47.208 --> 46:49.168
it created an alliance against him.

46:49.193 --> 46:50.969
Now you want us to rush into war

46:51.005 --> 46:53.223
because you see your
window of opportunity closing?

46:53.248 --> 46:55.007
The sheik chose Ihab,

46:55.042 --> 46:56.441
loud and clear.

46:56.477 --> 46:58.446
If he were alive,
I know what side he'd be on.

46:58.471 --> 46:59.785
We all do.

46:59.810 --> 47:02.441
- I stand with the sheik.
- The sheik's dead! Look at the facts.

47:02.466 --> 47:04.058
It's our decision now.

47:04.083 --> 47:05.217
Who's with me?

47:19.365 --> 47:21.465
(exhales)

47:21.501 --> 47:24.035
Now, where were we?

47:24.070 --> 47:26.570
MALOOF: But we will not be deterred.

47:26.605 --> 47:29.340
We will continue this fight,

47:29.375 --> 47:33.461
even into their own territory
until we eliminate this threat

47:33.486 --> 47:35.446
to our way of life.

47:35.481 --> 47:37.281
(turns off TV)

47:37.316 --> 47:39.198
Have you seen the latest polls?

47:39.223 --> 47:40.479
Yeah, I've seen them.

47:40.504 --> 47:44.031
It makes things complicated, the polls.

47:45.115 --> 47:47.435
The army's not inclined
to support anyone,

47:47.460 --> 47:49.894
just because they
happen to win the election.

47:51.063 --> 47:53.029
Really?

47:54.866 --> 47:56.433
Well...

47:57.542 --> 47:58.673
I don't think you're quite

47:58.698 --> 48:00.589
getting the hang of democracy, General.

48:00.614 --> 48:01.981
(scoffs)

48:03.849 --> 48:05.014
You may be right.

48:05.039 --> 48:06.104
A military coup?

48:06.129 --> 48:07.396
The army was never going

48:07.421 --> 48:08.568
to allow Leila Al Fayeed

48:08.593 --> 48:10.493
to succeed her husband.

48:10.715 --> 48:12.484
Just so you know.

48:12.751 --> 48:14.251
Yeah.

48:14.286 --> 48:15.718
Well, let me tell you what happens

48:15.754 --> 48:18.354
when you decide to exercise veto power

48:18.390 --> 48:20.122
over the will of the people,

48:20.157 --> 48:22.425
the American military goes home,

48:22.460 --> 48:23.970
and with it all of its equipment,

48:23.995 --> 48:25.561
all of its spare parts

48:25.597 --> 48:27.930
and all of its intelligence capabilities.

48:27.965 --> 48:31.534
So, then what kind of army would
you have in six months?

48:31.569 --> 48:34.136
Oh, I'm shocked, General.

48:34.171 --> 48:36.406
I thought we were allies.

48:37.241 --> 48:39.442
Oh, please.

48:46.918 --> 48:48.217
(knocking on door)

48:48.252 --> 48:49.754
Yes?

48:51.935 --> 48:54.044
I-I'm sorry. It's-it's
too late, we'll...

48:54.069 --> 48:55.336
It's okay.

48:59.029 --> 49:00.529
I was just...

49:01.632 --> 49:03.532
I wanted to see how you are.

49:03.567 --> 49:04.999
I saw the polls.

49:05.026 --> 49:06.523
I realize my mother's made things...

49:06.557 --> 49:07.989
I know.

49:12.075 --> 49:13.808
What?

49:13.833 --> 49:14.965
I know.

49:14.990 --> 49:16.490
She told me.

49:19.182 --> 49:21.316
I'm happy about it.

49:21.351 --> 49:23.452
I hope you are.

49:26.221 --> 49:28.556
I'm trying to process it.

49:29.358 --> 49:31.224
What it means.

49:31.260 --> 49:33.594
How much I've missed.

49:34.502 --> 49:36.602
How to tell everyone else in my life.

49:36.627 --> 49:38.293
Right.

49:38.318 --> 49:40.218
I know.

49:40.368 --> 49:42.133
And if it's too much, too late, I...

49:42.158 --> 49:44.792
No.

49:48.210 --> 49:49.777
You're my son.

50:03.558 --> 50:06.058
(knocking on door)

50:06.094 --> 50:07.712
Mr. President?

50:07.737 --> 50:08.798
A video...

50:08.823 --> 50:10.440
from Ihab bin Rashid.

50:10.465 --> 50:13.743
The President of Abuddin and
his American bombs have murdered

50:13.768 --> 50:17.871
Sheik Abdullah, leaving me
the leader of the Caliphate.

50:17.906 --> 50:21.040
For the first time since
Bassam Al Fayeed and I

50:21.075 --> 50:24.711
opposed each other,
we both have an army.

50:26.815 --> 50:30.383
In the name of the Prophet, Bassam,

50:30.418 --> 50:33.685
let's finish this once and for all.

50:39.459 --> 50:42.127
I'm going to war...

50:43.497 --> 50:44.993
...to avenge your death.

50:49.327 --> 50:51.509
You need to go now, honey.

50:51.896 --> 50:53.298
I need to sleep.

50:56.009 --> 50:57.500
Let me sleep.

